  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Delphi study on perioperative rehabilitation after single level lumbar arthrodesis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to engage all care providers in UZ Leuven who are at some point
      involved in the rehabilitation path related to single level lumbar arthrodesis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
